<HL>
   International:
   Aborigines Win
   Ban on a Mine
   In Australia
   ----
   By Elizabeth Main and Jane Blennerhassett
   Special to The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/19/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7
</SO>
<CO>
   A.NBH A.NDR BHP NEM
</CO>
